room_title: Escape room "Wild West" by Escape Thrill in Tampa
room_description: It’s August 2nd, 1876, you’re in a saloon in Deadwood located in the Black Hills of the Dakota Territory. “Wild Bill” Hickok, gunfighter, gambler and lawman, has just been shot dead from behind while playing poker by an unsuccessful gambler, Jack McCall, better known as “Crooked Nose Jack”. McCall fled the saloon, but not before locking everyone in. You must escape in time to apprehend McCall before he flees town and see justice is done.
